          {
            "id": "recItg17A6SCw8PHT",
            "term": 1,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] (Old Testament) Act out a memorable Bible reading from the term.\n[ ] (New Testament) Begin working on a \"picture biography\" of Jesus using your own brush drawings or fine art prints.\n[ ] (New Testament) Act out one of the miracles of Jesus."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 2,
        "title": "Term 2",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "rec2vOu7SHBLVc4LJ",
            "term": 2,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] (Bible) Visit a museum of antiquities to see artifacts from the time of Christ.\n[ ] (Bible) Learn the names of the books of the Bible. [\"The Best Books of the Bible\"](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=powlzb2Rfdw&ab_channel=JumpStart3) song can help.\n[ ] (Old Testament) Retell a memorable Bible reading from the term to a family member or friend.\n[ ] (New Testament) Continue working on a \"picture biography\" of Jesus using your own brush drawings or fine art prints.\n[ ] (New Testament) Act out one of the miracles of Jesus."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "term": 3,
        "title": "Term 3",
        "items": [
          {
            "id": "rec8VhtlgiAEbu3Sj",
            "term": 3,
            "sort": "",
            "content": "[ ] (Bible) Take a [virtual tour of Biblical sites](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nl5DNKf0mFw&t=13s&ab_channel=JohnDeLancey) in Israel. How many do you recognize from this year's readings?\n[ ] (Bible) Visit a [museum](https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.bibleplaces.com/us-museums-artifacts-biblical-world/&sa=D&source=editors&ust=1748367712641153&usg=AOvVaw0rhMobIU0hSuu13wR5ZW0Z) that houses artifacts from Ancient Israel.\n[ ] (Old Testament) Retell a memorable Bible reading from the term to a family member or friend.\n[ ] (New Testament) Create a \"[Resurrection Garden.](https://seedskidsworship.com/resurrection-garden/)\" (These can also be used as centerpieces for Easter dinner.)\n[ ] (New Testament) Spend time fishing as a family and try to name all the times fish or fishing are mentioned in this term's readings.\n[ ] (New Testament) Finish your \"picture biography\" of Jesus using your own brush drawings or fine art prints."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
